!! Workflow

# Use the graph index to pick a node.
# Follow upstream inputs and downstream outputs.
# Compare company/ticker exposure with the embedded charts.
# Add notes, sources, or new edges as tiddlers.

!! GitHub saving

If editing from the live GitHub Pages site, configure the built-in GitHub saver once in Control Panel → Saving → GitHub Saver. See [[GitHub Saver Setup]].
